(80, 4, '2015-08-26 07:26:21', '2015-08-26 15:26:21', '<h1>Inspections</h1>\r\n<p class=\"highlight\">Relying on in-house factory inspections can be a risk. Too often merchandise received is of inferior quality, incorrectly packaged, incorrectly labeled or short shipped.</p>\r\nWith supply chains stretching across the globe, the time required to return the merchandise, process a claim and allow vendors to rework orders can cost significant retail dollars.\r\n\r\nOmega provides you with comprehensive quality inspection services. Our 3rd party inspection teams are on the front line, working at your manufacturers, striving to assure that the goods you receive meet your exacting requirements.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href=\"https://local.omega.com/contact/\">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Inspections', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-26 07:26:21', '2015-08-26 15:26:21', '', 39, 'https://local.omega.com/39-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(81, 4, '2015-08-26 07:27:10', '2015-08-26 15:27:10', '<h1>Anti-Corruption</h1>\r\n<p class=\"highlight\">Fraud and corruption across supply chains is a serious risk and has enormous potential consequences to your business. Common corrupt practices include purchase orders being awarded to poorly qualified suppliers, factories with egregious ethical issues becoming part of your supply chain or defective shipments being passed by quality inspectors.</p>\r\nWhile these risks can never be eliminated it is imperative that you have the requisite controls in place across your business operations. Omega’s dedicated ethical monitoring team provides a broad range of integrity investigations services, such as conflicts of interest, bribery, and fraud, both internal and external, to companies who may not have the in-house resources to manage this risk themselves. Omega has unparalleled experience in developing and managing anti-corruption programs, programs which span more than 20 countries and a supply base in excess of 2,000 manufacturers.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href=\"https://local.omega.com/contact/\">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Anti-Corruption', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-26 07:27:10', '2015-08-26 15:27:10', '', 41, 'https://local.omega.com/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(82, 4, '2015-08-26 07:27:50', '2015-08-26 15:27:50', '<h1>Training</h1>\r\n<p class=\"highlight\">Achieving security and social compliance across a vast production network is a unique challenge. With factory security criteria under development and social compliance standards numerous, complicated and subject to change, many of your vendors are in need of guidance.</p>\r\nLeveraging our extensive remediation expertise, we operate our own proprietary training programs in which our expert social compliance and factory security teams will educate your vendors in the requisite procedures to ensure minimum standards are met.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href=\"https://local.omega.com/contact/\">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Training', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-26 07:27:50', '2015-08-26 15:27:50', '', 43, 'https://local.omega.com/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(83, 4, '2017-02-28 20:51:07', '2017-03-01 04:51:07', 'Omega goes beyond monitoring. We focus upon thorough assessments, comprehensive investigations, full disclosure and effective remediation. We strive to ensure that all parties, from manufacturers, trading entities, logistics providers, brands and retailers have full transparency over their supply chain partners, product and associates. We enable our clients to understand any shortcomings then provide them with the expertise to remediate effectively allowing them to operate their supply chains with complete confidence.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-02-28 20:51:07', '2017-03-01 04:51:07', '', 8, 'https://local.omega.com/8-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(84, 4, '2015-08-28 11:21:39', '2015-08-28 19:21:39', '<div class=\"hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg visible-xs banner_text\">every day the world\'s most trusted consumer brands put their faith in omega</div>\r\n<h1>About us</h1>\r\n<p class=\"highlight\">Every day many of the world\'s most trusted consumer brands put their faith in Omega to ensure the integrity of their global supply chains as they endeavor to work with partners who are secure, reliable, ethical and free from corrupt practices.</p>\r\nOmega goes beyond monitoring. We focus upon complete inspections, thorough investigations, full disclosure and effective remediation. We strive to ensure that all parties, from manufacturers, trading entities, logistics providers and brands have full transparency over their product, supply chain partners, employees and associates. We enable our clients to understand any shortcomings then provide them with the expertise to remediate effectively allowing them to operate their supply chains with complete confidence.', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-28 11:21:39', '2015-08-28 19:21:39', '', 8, 'https://local.omega.com/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(85, 4, '2015-08-28 11:28:41', '2015-08-28 19:28:41', '<div class=\"hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg visible-xs banner_text\"><h2>over 4,000</h2><p>supply chain audits across more than 20 countries each year</p></div>\r\n<h1>Anti-Corruption</h1>\r\n<p class=\"highlight\">Fraud and corruption across supply chains is a serious risk and has enormous potential consequences to your business. Common corrupt practices include purchase orders being awarded to poorly qualified suppliers, factories with egregious ethical issues becoming part of your supply chain or defective shipments being passed by quality inspectors.</p>\r\nWhile these risks can never be eliminated it is imperative that you have the requisite controls in place across your business operations. Omega’s dedicated ethical monitoring team provides a broad range of integrity investigations services, such as conflicts of interest, bribery, and fraud, both internal and external, to companies who may not have the in-house resources to manage this risk themselves. Omega has unparalleled experience in developing and managing anti-corruption programs, programs which span more than 20 countries and a supply base in excess of 2,000 manufacturers.\r\n\r\nFor more information on how Omega can support your business please <strong><a href=\"https://local.omega.com/contact/\">contact us</a></strong>.', 'Anti-Corruption', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-28 11:28:41', '2015-08-28 19:28:41', '', 41, 'https://local.omega.com/41-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
