g hours, within an attainable timeframe. Omega works with a number of brands who have adopted this approach and has seen gains in access to authentic records by up to 30%.\r\n\r\nOmega has vast experience in developing and managing social compliance audits programs across global supply chains. Should you wish to learn more about our services please contact us.', 'What role should factory auditing play in a robust, social compliance program?', 'Social compliance auditing regularly comes under criticism for being outmoded, ineffective and, even, counterproductive.  ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '169-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-12 20:40:00', '2015-10-13 04:40:00', '', 169, 'https://local.omega.com/169-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
