rams across complex supply chains. Should you require information on our services please <a href=\"https://local.omega.com/contact/\">contact us</a>.', '3 Ways to Maximize Return on Your Responsible Sourcing Program', 'Much more should be done, by brands and retailers, before, during and after the audit, to maximize return on their investment.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '318-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-17 22:52:02', '2016-03-18 06:52:02', '', 318, 'https://local.omega.com/318-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
