diting is imperfect, the need for measurement and verification remains crucial in any effective responsible sourcing program.  Much more should be done, by brands and retailers, before, during and after the audit, to maximize return on their investment.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '318-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-18 00:41:44', '2016-03-18 08:41:44', '', 318, 'https://local.omega.com/318-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
