. Should you require information on our services please <a href=\"https://local.omega.com/contact/\" target=\"_blank\">contact us</a>.', '3 Ways to Maximize Return on Your Responsible Sourcing Program', 'A Responsible Sourcing Program is a significant investment.  Much more should be done before, during and after the audit, to maximize return.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '318-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-18 00:53:40', '2016-03-18 08:53:40', '', 318, 'https://local.omega.com/318-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
