inking and bold leadership there is no reason why the next ten years cannot be even more productive than the last.', 'Improving Upon the Audit Model? 10 Years in the Responsible Sourcing Profession', 'Mark Evans, Omega\'s Director of Business Services, reflects and looks to the future after 10 years in the responsible sourcing profession.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '433-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-10 09:19:59', '2017-01-10 17:19:59', '', 433, 'https://local.omega.com/433-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
